\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{2}>\delta>0$
\end_inset

, we define the approximation vector 
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{v}^{(0)}=v^{(0)}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{v}^{(k)}=\mathtt{SelectVector}(\overline{v}^{(k-1)},v^{(0)},v^{(1)},\cdots,v^{(k)},\delta)$
\end_inset

.
