 The rest of the formula can be computed in 
\begin_inset Formula $O(T_{n,n,q}+T_{n,q,q})=O(T_{n,n,q})$
\end_inset

 time.
 In total, the runtime is 
\begin_inset Formula $O(T_{n,n,q})$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
